NAME
    Perinci::Sub::Property::cmdline - Specify command-line attributes

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.02 of Perinci::Sub::Property::cmdline
    (from Perl distribution Perinci-Sub-Property-cmdline), released on
    2014-10-28.

SYNOPSIS
    In function Rinci metadata:

     "cmdline.default_format" => "text",

DESCRIPTION
    Currently this property does nothing by itself, it is just a namespace
    for specifying command-line-related attributes (like shown in Synopsis).

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Perinci-Sub-Property-cmdline>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-Perinci-Sub-Property-cmdline>.

BUGS
